txt.en: 'You have done well, brother. Make haste, return to your post and send the hero who took your place back to me.'
You have successfully completed your patrol through the Ettenmoors.

'Trolls have been called from the north. We must redouble our efforts, else the Free Peoples here will fall, and Angmar will flood Eriador through the Trollshaws. Steel your nerve, brother, and know that the hero who stands at your post will not fail us.'
Patrol the Ettenmoors in search of the Enemy. You must patrol for 60 minutes. After 60 minutes you will be returned to your post.
